The paper deals with video question answering, which involves understanding both visual and linguistic information. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and multimedia (cs.MM). Among these, cs.CL and cs.CV are the most likely categories, as the paper focuses on language and vision processing.
